data.title: Techtron Engineering, Anoka
data.meta_description: Book a lab test with Techtron Engineering, a clinical laboratory offering a comprehensive array of routine and specialty lab testing services at 640 E Main St, Anoka, MN, 55303. For more information and to schedule a visit, call Techtron Engineering at  at (763) 712‑9502 .
data.text:
Techtron Engineering is an outpatient clinical laboratory and testing facility in Anoka offering an array of on-demand lab testing services. Depending on the necessary test, patients are either referred to Techtron Engineering by a qualified provider, or can just with test results available as quickly as the same day.

They are open 5 days a week, including today from 8:00AM to 4:30PM . Techtron Engineering offers you the ability to book online in advance through Solv prior to arriving at the lab, which should cut your wait time considerably and get you on with your day more quickly.
